data.description: Charming home in Wynston with downstairs primary bedroom! Move-in ready! New carpets & fresh paint. New HVAC 2022, new energy-efficient windows 2021, new stove & microwave 2021, new fridge 2020, new roof 2020, new solar panels 2018. Open floor plan with soaring ceilings, and ceiling fans throughout. Kitchen is open to living  room and breakfast area, with separate dining room & trey ceiling. Dual sink vanity in primary bath with garden tub, separate shower and walk-in closet. 2nd floor bonus room is fully functional as 4th bedroom. 2 car garage. 10’ x 18’ patio in back with partially fenced yard. Pool community!
